data.description:
A great view of Upper Prior Lake from the living room! This is a unique property that includes deeded lake front with your own private boat slip, plus a shared lot on Twin Island. Walk to your own boat lift! See lot lines in the photos. Motivated Seller! The house is on a .42 acre lot bordering an undeveloped county lot. Over 2000 Sq/ft. Walkout Lower Level. Many updates throughout the home. New roof in 2019, Stainless Kitchen appliances 2019+, Fresh Paint 2023, Water Heater 2019, updated electrical and much more.  Why drive north for hours to the cabin when you can live at "The Lake" right here!? Fish every morning before you go to work! Just walk to your boat and go.
Don't miss out on this extraordinary opportunity! Make sure to schedule a visit to fully appreciate all that this property has to offer.
